{
  "stem": "3964.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where did it come from?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We knew the Germans was-- were not that generous or hospitable to us to give us a welcoming party.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And after discussions-- discussions went on in our apartment, some of the older people and my father, the conclusion they arrived at, that the food was poisoned, that they put the food there because we were hungry, we hadn't eaten for several days, that we were ravished, we would consume the food and we would die.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And nobody touched the food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody ate anything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Food was left there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And nighttime came, we went to sleep exhausted.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the next morning, we got up and ventured out of the house we were in, and so did other people from our group.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we found out that there was another group of German Jews in the ghetto, who just had arrived two days prior to our arrival.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they were right in the next block, so to speak, from us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we found out from them that the food, which was left behind [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] was food which was on a table from Latvian Jews who had lived in those houses prior to our arrival, two days prior to our arrival, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that they had been taken out of those houses, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] and they had been shot.",
      "word_count": 69
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They had been killed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] And we figured out after that, you know, food was of prime importance.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Shocked, unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But we realized then that the food which was left behind was good food and that we could eat it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Everything was frozen, obviously.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was cold.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
